‚úÖ 2.3 Start a Project
Endpoint: /api/project/start

Method: POST

Request Body:

json
Copy
Edit
{
  "user_id": "12345",
  "project_id": "98765"
}
Response:

json
Copy
Edit
{
  "message": "Project started successfully",
  "project_id": "98765",
  "status": "In Progress"
}
‚úÖ 2.4 Submit Project for Review
Endpoint: /api/project/submit/{project_id}

Method: POST

Headers:

makefile
Copy
Edit
Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>
Request Body:

json
Copy
Edit
{
  "submission_url": "https://github.com/user/project-repo",
  "comments": "Completed all tasks and tested the chatbot."
}
Response:

json
Copy
Edit
{
  "message": "Project submitted successfully. Awaiting review."
}
